# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:34
translate spanish hwb_s18_1998ef28:

    # "A brisk wind curls around me as I step out onto a patch of dirt that can barely be called a parking spot, in a place that can barely be called a campground."
    "Un viento rápido se arremolina a mi alrededor mientras salgo a un pedazo de tierra que apenas puede llamarse estacionamiento, en un lugar que apenas puede llamarse campamento."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:36
translate spanish hwb_s18_31cf67a4:

    # "Misty curtains have settled over the nearby hills and mountains and small specks of leftover morning dew occasionally drip on me from above."
    "Cortinas de niebla se han posado sobre las colinas y montañas cercanas, y pequeñas gotas de rocío matutino caen ocasionalmente sobre mí desde arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:38
translate spanish hwb_s18_e4f1a298:

    # "Bending down, I drop my backpack and pull on the tongue of my ‘sorta-new’ hiking boots. A little big, but they’ll work."
    "Agachándome, dejo caer mi mochila y tiro de la lengüeta de mis botas de senderismo «casi nuevas». Un poco grandes, pero servirán."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:40
translate spanish hwb_s18_135cc3fb:

    # "Considering these came from the stash of supplies we borrowed from Mariah in New Mexico... her feet must be freaking huge."
    "Considerando que estas son del lote de suministros que tomamos prestados de Mariah en Nuevo México... sus pies deben ser enormes."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:55
translate spanish hwb_s18_f664a0b9:

    # Marina "All set?"
    Marina "Все готово?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:61
translate spanish hwb_s18_bec570d0:

    # "Marina is standing behind me, frowning at her own velcro-strapped boots."
    "Marina está detrás de mí, frunciendo el ceño ante sus propias botas con cierre de velcro."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s18_8fb314d0:

    # Amber "Just about. These boots are pretty big, though."
    Amber "Почти. Эти ботинки достаточно велики."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:70
translate spanish hwb_s18_cbcbbf1f:

    # Marina "You think so? They feel a bit snug to me."
    Marina "Думаешь? А мне кажется, они плотно сидят."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:72
translate spanish hwb_s18_6629f575:

    # "Sheesh, never mind about Mariah."
    "Rayos, olvida lo de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:81
translate spanish hwb_s18_aff91f04:

    # Amber "Hey, forget about the treasure. Let’s just dress you up as Bigfoot and turn you in for a cash reward."
    Amber "Эй, забудь о сокровище. Давай просто переоденем тебя в Снежного Человека и сдадим за награду."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s18_2d037a7b:

    # "The joke is awful and I know it. Still, Marina plays along, sticking her tongue out in a half-playful manner before she forces a tired smile. The whole time, she doesn't make eye contact."
    "El chiste es malo y lo sé. Aun así, Marina sigue el juego, sacando la lengua de forma medio juguetona antes de forzar una sonrisa cansada. Todo el tiempo, no hace contacto visual."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s18_085503cd:

    # "So much for lightening the mood."
    "Tanto para aligerar el ambiente."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s18_738f9f8b:

    # "Last night's sudden tension is still present. Even though we try to ignore it, or pretend it isn't there, we both know."
    "La tensión repentina de anoche sigue presente. Aunque intentamos ignorarla, o fingir que no está, ambos lo sabemos."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:97
translate spanish hwb_s18_b643ec62:

    # "We both can't look at each other directly, and our conversation feels awkward and stilted."
    "Ambos no podemos mirarnos directamente, y nuestra conversación se siente incómoda y forzada."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s18_7a43da7d:

    # "But we pretend everything's normal as we try to put on our best performances and reenact our usual routine."
    "Pero fingimos que todo es normal mientras intentamos dar lo mejor de nosotros y recrear nuestra rutina habitual."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s18_52637ed0:

    # Marina "So how long is the hike?"
    Marina "Итак, как долго будет длиться наш поход?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s18_96888310:

    # Amber "The brochure said about ninety minutes each way. Might take even longer in this weather."
    Amber "В брошюре сказано, что на каждый путь потребуется около девяносто минут. Учитывая погоду, может выйти даже дольше."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:111
translate spanish hwb_s18_4b39cc35:

    # Marina "Oh…"
    Marina "Ох…"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s18_4e50b0c9:

    # "I can feel the gulf between us. It's like yet another canyon, except I don't know how to cross this one."
    "Puedo sentir el abismo entre nosotras. Es como otro cañón, excepto que no sé cómo cruzar este."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s18_18df5c70:

    # Marina "The picture in the brochure was super pretty. Angel’s Landing, right?"
    Marina "Фотография в брошюре была безумно красивая. Приют Ангелов, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s18_a1e11f55:

    # "Now it's her turn to try and lighten the mood."
    "Ahora es su turno de intentar aligerar el ambiente."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s18_bf39b97f:

    # "I hate how we're both too afraid to just address the issue."
    "Odio cómo ambas tenemos demasiado miedo para simplemente abordar el problema."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s18_d7bcac82:

    # "But I'm just as guilty as she is here."
    "Pero yo soy tan culpable como ella aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s18_f123f03a:

    # "I sigh and play along as best I can."
    "Suspiro y sigo el juego lo mejor que puedo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s18_684e8b3f:

    # Amber "Yeah, it's nice."
    Amber "Да, там красиво."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s18_d55715dc:

    # Amber "It’s supposed to be the most scenic view in Zion."
    Amber "Это должен быть самый живописный вид в Зайоне."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s18_fa595c79:

    # "That’s what Gramps told me anyway."
    "Eso fue lo que el abuelo me dijo, al menos."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s18_b5f42d92:

    # "This hike was one of his favorites. Said the view is so lush; that there's so many trees and plants, that he discovered several new shades of green up there."
    "Esta caminata era una de sus favoritas. Decía que la vista es tan frondosa; que hay tantos árboles y plantas, que descubrió varios tonos nuevos de verde allá arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s18_e33b7cdd:

    # "It was one of the spots that he was most looking forward to visiting with me."
    "Era uno de los lugares que más esperaba visitar conmigo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s18_2ad25d59:

    # "I glance back up at the mountains. The mist doesn’t look like it will clear anytime soon. In fact, it seems to be swallowing up more of the landscape."
    "Vuelvo a mirar hacia las montañas. La niebla no parece que se despejará pronto. De hecho, parece estar tragándose más del paisaje."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s18_03a6a7a1:

    # "It's got Marina's attention too. She stares up as if she's picking out specific details in the fog."
    "También tiene la atención de Marina. Ella mira hacia arriba como si estuviera distinguiendo detalles específicos en la niebla."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s18_9c1f2bb1:

    # "While she's distracted, I let my gaze rove over her again. Guiltily, like I'm sneaking glances, but I don't care."
    "Mientras está distraída, dejo que mi mirada recorra su figura otra vez. Culposamente, como si estuviera robando miradas, pero no me importa."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s18_29f3940a:

    # "Admiring the sweep of her shoulders down into her collarbone, and the rest of the curves of her body."
    "Admirando la curva de sus hombros hasta su clavícula, y el resto de las curvas de su cuerpo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s18_25eb7477:

    # "I let myself examine her like I did when we first met, and like I've been consciously abstaining from. Looking her over like it doesn't matter if she catches me anymore."
    "Me permito examinarla como cuando nos conocimos, y como he estado abstrayéndome conscientemente de hacerlo. Mirándola como si ya no importara que me descubra."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s18_2b91be7e:

    # "She doesn't, though. I may as well as be invisible to her right now while she studies the mountaintops."
    "Pero no lo hace. Podría ser invisible para ella ahora mismo mientras estudia las cimas de las montañas."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s18_c6474d99:

    # "And I want her to pay attention to me."
    "Y quiero que me preste atención."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s18_d0f085f7:

    # "She’s wearing her usual boutique brand clothes. Their cute frilliness is just as perfect as ever for Marina, but they clash with the clunkiness of the ugly brown boots."
    "Lleva su ropa habitual de boutique. Su lindo vuelo es tan perfecto como siempre para Marina, pero choca con la torpeza de las feas botas marrones."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:161
translate spanish hwb_s18_1cfb7087:

    # Amber "You sure you wanna wear that? They might just get in the way."
    Amber "Ты уверена, что пойдешь в этом? В такой одежде тебе может быть неудобно."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:165
translate spanish hwb_s18_c833de50:

    # "She gasps, almost offended by the suggestion that she wear anything else."
    "Jadea, casi ofendida por la sugerencia de que use otra cosa."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s18_7b189251:

    # Marina "But my skirt is so comfy! Aren’t you supposed to wear comfy clothes on hikes?"
    Marina "Но мне так удобно в этой юбке! Разве в походы не принято надевать удобную одежду?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:171
translate spanish hwb_s18_1fb0f56f:

    # Marina "Besides! With a name like Angel’s Landing it has to be pretty relaxing."
    Marina "Кроме того! Поход к месту с названием “Приют Ангелов” просто обязан быть легким и приятным."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:175
translate spanish hwb_s18_cc4bc962:

    # "She gives me a big, honest smile, tipping her head to the hills."
    "Me dedica una gran sonrisa sincera, inclinando la cabeza hacia las colinas."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s18_f0588c45:

    # "It's the first real smile I've seen from her all day."
    "Es la primera sonrisa real que le veo en todo el día."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:181
translate spanish hwb_s18_39367cfb:

    # Marina "So what’re we waiting for? Let’s go!"
    Marina "Так чего мы ждем? Вперед!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s18_573254fc:

    # "I melt, letting her skewed reasoning fall to the wayside just this once. Warm fuzzies and a goofy grin take over my dour mood. Just for a moment."
    "Me derrito, dejando de lado su lógica torcida solo por esta vez. Una calidez difusa y una sonrisa tonta se apoderan de mi mal humor. Solo por un momento."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:189
translate spanish hwb_s18_4cc5bc27:

    # Amber "Alright, but no whining if they end up being a problem!"
    Amber "Хорошо, но только не жалуйся потом, если эти рюши вдруг станут проблемой!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:193
translate spanish hwb_s18_ae23116c:

    # "Slinging the backpack over my shoulder, we head for the shuttle that leads to the trail."
    "Colgando la mochila al hombro, nos dirigimos al transporte que lleva al sendero."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:195
translate spanish hwb_s18_859ebea9:

    # "Logs and a stone fire pit adorn the side of each lot that we pass."
    "Troncos y un fogón de piedra adornan el costado de cada parcela que pasamos."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s18_80aa5f8a:

    # "Maybe when we get back we’ll go to the camp store and pick up some supplies to roast marshmallows."
    "Quizás cuando volvamos vayamos a la tienda del campamento y compremos provisiones para asar malvaviscos."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:199
translate spanish hwb_s18_3ed58c68:

    # "I think she'd like that."
    "Creo que a ella le gustaría eso."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s18_c0bb274b:

    # "Marina’s heavy breathing guides me as we slog our way uphill, the previous light mist having now morphed into a thick and dreary fog."
    "La respiración pesada de Marina me guía mientras subimos la cuesta, la niebla ligera de antes se ha convertido en una espesa y lúgubre bruma."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:229
translate spanish hwb_s18_b2c8e3f0:

    # "I cling to the chained railing as I stumble my way up the trail of rocks. It's the only protection from the sheer drop-off beside us."
    "Me aferro a la barandilla encadenada mientras tropiezo por el sendero de rocas. Es la única protección contra el precipicio que tenemos al lado."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:231
translate spanish hwb_s18_f64340c5:

    # "All it would take is one slip for me to take a nosedive into the valley below, and I wouldn’t even see it coming."
    "Solo bastaría un resbalón para que me precipite al valle de abajo, y ni siquiera lo vería venir."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:233
translate spanish hwb_s18_6f19d122:

    # "Turns out, the fluffy and enticing name ‘Angel’s Landing’ doesn’t come with the ‘relaxing stroll’ Marina was hoping for."
    "Resulta que el esponjoso y tentador nombre 'El Aterrizaje del Ángel' no viene con el 'paseo relajante' que Marina esperaba."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:235
translate spanish hwb_s18_59b85fc0:

    # "This feels more like a ghastly death march. My sweat-drenched legs feel like pudding under the anchor that is a measly five pound backpack."
    "Esto se siente más como una marcha fúnebre espantosa. Mis piernas empapadas de sudor se sienten como pudín bajo el ancla de una mochila de apenas cinco libras."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:237
translate spanish hwb_s18_21ca5afe:

    # "No one else on the shuttle even bothered to attempt the hike alongside us."
    "Nadie más en el transporte siquiera se molestó en intentar la caminata junto a nosotras."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:239
translate spanish hwb_s18_248847cf:

    # "I attempt to form words between pained breaths, feeling like a rock is being smashed into my lungs with each step."
    "Intento formar palabras entre respiraciones dolorosas, sintiendo como si una roca se estrellara contra mis pulmones con cada paso."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:241
translate spanish hwb_s18_61a04a77:

    # Amber "We should turn back."
    Amber "Мы должны повернуть назад."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:243
translate spanish hwb_s18_c030e2f8:

    # Amber "Can’t see jack."
    Amber "Я не вижу подъемника."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:245
translate spanish hwb_s18_9ad9acee:

    # Amber "It’s not safe up here."
    Amber "Тут не безопасно."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:247
translate spanish hwb_s18_e0508e49:

    # Marina "What?"
    Marina "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:249
translate spanish hwb_s18_166096b4:

    # "She sounds like she’s doing about as well as me, echoing the same lung-puncturing gasps."
    "Suena como si estuviera tan mal como yo, haciendo eco de los mismos jadeos que perforan los pulmones."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:251
translate spanish hwb_s18_48ab62f3:

    # Marina "But we’re so close!"
    Marina "Но мы уже так близко!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:253
translate spanish hwb_s18_90360629:

    # Marina "There’s no way we’re not almost there!"
    Marina "Мы ведь почти добрались!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s18_e5940948:

    # "We stop, collapsing against our knees as we try to catch our breath."
    "Nos detenemos, desplomándonos sobre nuestras rodillas mientras intentamos recuperar el aliento."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s18_00c1c755:

    # Amber "Not gonna mean a whole lot if we end up falling off a cliff."
    Amber "Все это не будет иметь никакого значения, если мы упадем с обрыва."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:275
translate spanish hwb_s18_1f91ae51:

    # Marina "I thought-"
    Marina "Я думала-"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:277
translate spanish hwb_s18_b92724a2:

    # Marina "You were-"
    Marina "Что ты-"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:279
translate spanish hwb_s18_0fa8353b:

    # Marina "The one who wanted-"
    Marina "Что именно ты хотела-"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:281
translate spanish hwb_s18_c59f1d31:

    # Marina "To do this so bad."
    Marina "Этого так сильно."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:283
translate spanish hwb_s18_b985b128:

    # "Every couple words are punctuated by her gasping for breath."
    "Cada par de palabras son interrumpidas por su jadeo por aire."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s18_b610ac08:

    # Amber "Yeah, but…"
    Amber "Да, но…"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s18_ed6775db:

    # Marina "Amber… please."
    Marina "Эмбер… пожалуйста."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:295
translate spanish hwb_s18_5c28df93:

    # Marina "Let's keep going."
    Marina "Давай продолжим подниматься."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s18_a78d9b87:

    # "Her voice is a whimper, fragile and meek. I fold."
    "Su voz es un gemido, frágil y dócil. Me rindo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s18_c7132439:

    # Amber "Okay, okay."
    Amber "Ладно, ладно."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s18_184b857a:

    # "Marina has a way of making me shut up when she wants to. Whether she knows it or not."
    "Marina tiene una forma de hacerme callar cuando quiere. Lo sepa o no."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:317
translate spanish hwb_s18_54369ec4:

    # "Today, it doesn't make a difference."
    "Hoy, no hace ninguna diferencia."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:319
translate spanish hwb_s18_4dd70de5:

    # "I’m not going to be the one who makes things worse."
    "No voy a ser yo quien empeore las cosas."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:321
translate spanish hwb_s18_1ca8d9d7:

    # "She’s wrong about one thing, though—I wasn’t the one who wanted to hike up here."
    "Aunque se equivoca en una cosa: yo no fui quien quiso subir hasta aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:325
translate spanish hwb_s18_d6621094:

    # "Gramps was."
    "Fue el abuelo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:329
translate spanish hwb_s18_3383dabb:

    # "It gets easier after our break."
    "Se vuelve más fácil después de nuestro descanso."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:333
translate spanish hwb_s18_28a6fff4:

    # "The trail begins to plateau and the steepness evens out, fading behind us until the return trip."
    "El sendero empieza a nivelarse y la pendiente se suaviza, quedando atrás hasta el regreso."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s18_cf55dfcb:

    # Marina "Ooooh! I think we’re already here!"
    Marina "Ооооох! Я думаю, мы почти пришли!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:343
translate spanish hwb_s18_fedcfd9b:

    # Marina "See! What did I tell you?"
    Marina "Видишь! Что я тебе говорила!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:348
translate spanish hwb_s18_d80042ea:

    # "Marina darts ahead, disappearing into the fog so she can look at the mythical view that the brochure and I have preached to her, and Gramps to me."
    "Marina se adelanta rápido, desapareciendo en la niebla para poder ver la vista mítica que el folleto y yo le hemos predicado, y el abuelo a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s18_6eb29fb1:

    # "But if my suspicions are right, this weather and the view aren’t going to be very compatible."
    "Pero si mis sospechas son correctas, este clima y la vista no van a ser muy compatibles."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:355
translate spanish hwb_s18_9669a290:

    # "Following behind, I step out of the cloudy murk and into an area that offers only slightly more visibility."
    "Siguiéndola detrás, salgo de la bruma nublada y entro en un área que ofrece solo un poco más de visibilidad."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:404
translate spanish hwb_s18_5196ab28:

    # "Marina stands still on the center of the cliff, her hand clutched to her heart."
    "Marina se queda quieta en el centro del acantilado, con la mano apretada contra el corazón."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s18_2aaf8e92:

    # "What should've been a bird's eye view of Zion is nothing but a sea of fog."
    "Lo que debería haber sido una vista panorámica de Zion no es más que un mar de niebla."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:408
translate spanish hwb_s18_25953fd8:

    # "The lush greenery and full valleys are invisible. Only a few overgrown bushes and some rocky points peek out above the clouds."
    "El verdor exuberante y los valles completos son invisibles. Solo unos arbustos crecidos y algunos picos rocosos asoman por encima de las nubes."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s18_7c502f3b:

    # "I was expecting it, but the sight itself really is numbing."
    "Me lo esperaba, pero la vista en sí realmente es entumecedora."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s18_fe904250:

    # "The hollowness in my stomach, the one I’ve gotten so used to feeling, rears its head once again, only intensified by Marina’s silence, any expression shrouded by her bangs as she tilts her head down."
    "El vacío en mi estómago, al que ya me he acostumbrado tanto, asoma la cabeza una vez más, solo intensificado por el silencio de Marina, cualquier expresión oculta por su flequillo mientras inclina la cabeza hacia abajo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s18_927286b4:

    # Amber "Sorry."
    Amber "Прости."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s18_cec02d81:

    # "Gently, she shakes her head."
    "Suavemente, niega con la cabeza."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s18_aff077c3:

    # Marina "Don’t worry about it. It’s not your fault."
    Marina "Не переживай насчет этого. Это не твоя вина."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:432
translate spanish hwb_s18_aed42a12:

    # Marina "You tried to warn me."
    Marina "Ты пыталась предупредить меня."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:434
translate spanish hwb_s18_8313149b:

    # Amber "Marina..."
    Amber "Марина..."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s18_156b662b:

    # "But I don't know what to say."
    "Pero no sé qué decir."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s18_b1fdad24:

    # "I'm disappointed too."
    "También estoy decepcionada."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s18_f08f9864:

    # "There were a lot of places Gramps always talked about visiting."
    "Había muchos lugares de los que el abuelo siempre hablaba de visitar."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s18_3194d598:

    # "\"After we settle down and kick back for a few years.\""
    "\"Después de que nos establezcamos y nos relajemos por unos años.\""

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s18_1de2dcb4:

    # "\"After I finish repairing the RV.\""
    "\"Después de que termine de reparar la casa rodante.\""

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s18_4f2397e9:

    # "\"After I get better.\""
    "\"Después de que mejore.\""

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s18_9b151b6f:

    # "This place came up more than the others, though."
    "Este lugar surgió más que los otros, sin embargo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s18_aad680f5:

    # "Not just Zion, but the Landing. Kept saying we were going to hike up here, have a picnic, maybe watch the sun come up."
    "No solo Zion, sino el Aterrizaje. Seguía diciendo que íbamos a subir hasta aquí, hacer un picnic, tal vez ver salir el sol."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s18_bc68c0b7:

    # "A slight smile comes to my face as I think about him trying to make that hike. I'd have liked to see the geezer try."
    "Una leve sonrisa se dibuja en mi rostro mientras pienso en él intentando hacer esa caminata. Me habría gustado ver al viejo intentarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s18_5bb07e13:

    # "While I'm not a big enough sap to try and make all of my and Gramps' plans happen now, it would've been nice to see the view."
    "Aunque no soy tan sentimental como para intentar cumplir todos los planes del abuelo y míos ahora, habría sido agradable ver la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:460
translate spanish hwb_s18_bb3959b0:

    # "With Gramps, Marina and everything that’s happened over the past month, it just seemed fitting to make the trip."
    "Con el abuelo, Marina y todo lo que ha pasado en el último mes, parecía adecuado hacer el viaje."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s18_c85552cd:

    # "Angel’s Landing."
    "El Mirador del Ángel."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:464
translate spanish hwb_s18_b41db96a:

    # "I glance back to Marina, the hand that was clutched to her chest now stretched outwards, grasping at the empty air. A slight breeze blows through, ruffling her hair."
    "Miro hacia atrás a Marina, la mano que tenía apretada contra el pecho ahora se extiende hacia afuera, aferrándose al aire vacío. Una ligera brisa sopla, despeinándole el cabello."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s18_30b4666f:

    # "She looks beautiful."
    "Se ve hermosa."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s18_0f868a5a:

    # "She looks..."
    "Se ve..."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:470
translate spanish hwb_s18_5703b330:

    # "Angelic."
    "Angelical."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s18_8601efe7:

    # "I didn't go to church much as a kid, but she looks like someone I’d see on a stained glass window. Right next to a rendition of Calvary or Skull Hill."
    "No iba mucho a la iglesia cuando era niña, pero parece alguien que vería en una vidriera. Justo al lado de una representación del Calvario o la Colina del Cráneo."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:476
translate spanish hwb_s18_e0100aef:

    # "It’s frustrating to have come this far for nothing."
    "Es frustrante haber llegado tan lejos para nada."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s18_d86f2353:

    # "But is it because of the fog?"
    "¿Pero es por la niebla?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s18_6995e41a:

    # "Because of Gramps?"
    "¿Por el Abuelo?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:482
translate spanish hwb_s18_f0a8befb:

    # "Or because of Marina?"
    "¿O por Marina?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s18_9db15fb8:

    # "My teeth grit, grinding against each other under what feels like an unimaginable weight."
    "Mis dientes rechinan, moliéndose entre sí bajo lo que parece un peso inimaginable."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s18_b755fe21:

    # Amber "C’mon, let's go."
    Amber "Ладно, пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:495
translate spanish hwb_s18_a7e5f1b0:

    # "I turn around and begin down the slope. There’s nothing else worth seeing up here."
    "Me doy la vuelta y empiezo a bajar la pendiente. No hay nada más que valga la pena ver aquí arriba."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:497
translate spanish hwb_s18_08bd1f9e:

    # "Marina doesn’t follow. No spirited footsteps trailing behind me. No speeding bullet blazing ahead."
    "Marina no me sigue. Ni pasos animados detrás de mí. Ni una bala veloz adelantándose."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:502
translate spanish hwb_s18_0f361d74:

    # Amber "Marina, we’re going!"
    Amber "Марина, мы уходим!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:504
translate spanish hwb_s18_928a25c2:

    # "It comes out with more bite than I intended, but I don’t care. I just want to get out of here now."
    "Sale con más mordacidad de la que pretendía, pero no me importa. Solo quiero salir de aquí ahora."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:506
translate spanish hwb_s18_277a5d77:

    # "Marina is hesitant to answer, but eventually manages to spit it out, sounding more like a question than an actual statement."
    "Marina duda en responder, pero finalmente logra soltarlo, sonando más como una pregunta que como una afirmación real."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:510
translate spanish hwb_s18_cfbffb7b:

    # Marina "I don’t want to."
    Marina "Я не хочу."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:514
translate spanish hwb_s18_5f1d9671:

    # Amber "What?"
    Amber "Что?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:516
translate spanish hwb_s18_3a93f3de:

    # Marina "I don’t want to leave."
    Marina "Я не хочу уходить."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:518
translate spanish hwb_s18_12cd616c:

    # Marina "Not yet, anyway."
    Marina "По крайней мере, не сейчас."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:520
translate spanish hwb_s18_45a6457c:

    # "Annoyed, I turn back to her for an explanation, only to be greeted by a pleading look instead."
    "Molesta, me giro hacia ella para pedirle una explicación, solo para encontrarme con una mirada suplicante en su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:524
translate spanish hwb_s18_803a1951:

    # Marina "I’m used to it by now, I know I am. But do you think we could wait a little longer, just to see if the fog clears?"
    Marina "Я уже привыкла к такому, я знаю, что привыкла. Но, может быть, мы могли бы  задержаться еще на чуть-чуть, чтобы подождать, пока туман рассеется?"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s18_5e01b588:

    # "I don't know what 'it' is."
    "No sé qué es \"eso\"."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s18_a79f520d:

    # "I respond with a blank stare."
    "Respondo con una mirada en blanco."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:532
translate spanish hwb_s18_bc5eaa9b:

    # "It’s like she’s not even talking to me."
    "Es como si ni siquiera me estuviera hablando a mí."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s18_2ca97f79:

    # Amber "Don’t be stupid."
    Amber "Не глупи."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:544
translate spanish hwb_s18_9253c056:

    # "I start back down the hill, not bothering to wait for Marina this time."
    "Empiezo a bajar la colina, sin molestarme en esperar a Marina esta vez."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:548
translate spanish hwb_s18_90898ea7:

    # Amber "It’s past noon. If it hasn’t cleared by now then it’s not going to anytime soon."
    Amber "Уже за полдень. Если он не рассеялся к этому времени, значит, в ближайшее время ничего не изменится."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:550
translate spanish hwb_s18_eef50d29:

    # "So much for not making things worse."
    "Tanto para no empeorar las cosas."

translate spanish strings:

    # script/hwb_s18.rpy:213
    old "Climbing up to Angel's Landing"
    new "Climbing up to Angel's Landing"

    # script/hwb_s18.rpy:602
    old "Climbing down to the RV"
    new "Climbing down to the RV"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:538
translate spanish hwb_s18_8ab322ca:

    # "Well, except for this weird girl who keeps floating around. She seems kind of cool."
    "Bueno, excepto por esta chica rara que no deja de flotar por ahí. Parece bastante genial."

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:548
translate spanish strings:
    old "Zion"
    new "Зайон"
translate spanish zion_line:

    # "Zion" "Yaaaaaay!"
    Zion "Ура!"

# game/script/hwb_s18.rpy:554
translate spanish hwb_s18_48a7b601:

    # "Wow, she sounds a lot like Tess."
    "Vaya, suena muy parecida a Tess."

